ed="T" n="0880c21"/><persName key="A013737">釋明準</persName>者，不詳氏族，生緣本<placeName key="PL000000014700"><placeName>天台</placeName><placeName>靈墟道場</placeName></placeName>，<lb
ed="T" n="0880c22"/>出俗遊方。至<ref type="place" target="#PL000000042189">京邑</ref>，觀古之神僧<persName key="A013739">智苑</persName>於<placeName key="PL000000002485"><anchor xml:id="beg0880sgsz10"/><choice resp="PC-JK-MB"><sic>苑</sic><corr>范</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0880sgsz10"/><lb
ed="T" n="0880c23"/>陽</placeName><ref type="place" target="#PL000000000447">北山</ref><ptr target="#n3369"/>刊石寫經、灌鐵，以俟<persName key="A001428">慈氏</persName>下生，免<lb
ed="T" n="0880c24"/>水火之虞<ptr target="#n3371"/>。又<placeName key="PL000000023652"><placeName>東洛</placeName><placeName>長壽寺</placeName></placeName>寫《華嚴》，<placeName key="PL000000023661">聖善寺</placeName>寫<lb
ed="T" n="0880c25"/>《法華》，<placeName key="PL000000023611">嵩山嶽寺</placeName>寫《楞伽》，悉刊貞珉<ptr type="glossary" target="#g2190"/>，皆圖不<lb
ed="T" n="0880c26"/>朽。<persName key="A013737">準</persName>遂於<date from-iso="+0798-01-26" key="j20125492012578" to-iso="+0798-02-24"><name>貞元</name>戊寅歲春正月</date>，見寺僧鏨<lb
ed="T" n="0880c27"/>山攻石，石悉頑惡，知匠氏不虔，山靈祕吝。<lb
ed="T" n="0880c28"/>時<persName key="A013737">準</persName>疏告陰靈，請禆善務。俄於定中見若<lb
ed="T" n="0880c29"/><anchor xml:id="beg0880sgsz11"/>干<anchor xml:id="end0880sgsz11"/>幅貯無量石<ptr target="#n3372"/>，冥冥之間，如有宰割，皆中<pb ed="T" n="0881a" xml:id="T50.2061.0881a"/><lb
ed="T" n="0881a01"/>刻字。時連率<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1521"/><placeName key="PL000000002513">博陵</placeName><name>崔</name>公<ptr target="#n3373"/>激勸幕府參佐各<lb
ed="T" n="0881a02"/>書一品，從〈序〉至〈勸發〉<ptr target="#n3374"/>，凡二十八。圜廊挺立，<lb
ed="T" n="0881a03"/>不朞畢工。<persName key="A013737">準</persName>之化人，皆此類也。<date key="j20157082015737" notAfter-iso="+0806-10-19" notBefore-iso="+0806-09-20"><name>元和</name>元年<lb
ed="T" n="0881a04"/>八月</date>中也。後不詳終所。</p>
